      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046920&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7705&rangeEnd=7777",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/af232d00813ab78d4g010f6f?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7705&rangeEnd=7777"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046920_6_17851-17915",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "17851-17915",
      "markText": "未来的中国，一定是一个超越乡土、超越血缘、超越宗族、超越宗教，能包容广土众民、众多信仰的大国，怎么能用狭隘的民族主义束缚自己呢？",
